title: Aliens.vs.Predator.MULTi8-PROPHET
description:
Aliens vs. Predator (c) SEGA

release date: August 2769
protection: Steam + CEG
# of discs: 1
languages: EN/FR/DE/IT/ES/PL/RU/CZ

Bringing the legendary war between two of
science-fiction's most popular characters to FPS
fans, AvP delivers three outstanding single player
campaigns and provides untold hours of unique 3-way
multiplayer gaming. Experience distinctly new and
thrilling first person gameplay as you survive
hunt and prey in the deadly jungles and swamps
surrounding the damned colony of Freya's Prospect

This release also includes DLCs:

* Swarm Map Pack DLC
* Bughunt Map Pack DLC

1- Unpack, burn or mount
2- Install the game
3- Copy the cracked content from PROPHET dir
4- Go To Hell!
